# MIS Positioning

## Core Positioning

Mission Integrity System (MIS) V1 is an exploration of the same deterministic classification philosophy applied to a different domain.

It extends principles commonly applied in:

- financial governance
- enterprise data systems
- transformation and control frameworks

into a simulated mission environment.

The through-line is not UAV development.

The through-line is deterministic classification of trust under degradation.

